JH - updated to include slack email alert to manager of case owner for cancel cases
BW - 6/14/24 - Replaced old SaaS Funnel Stage form CF with new SaaS Funnel Stage on the School Object
06/25/24 - PE - Updated flow to always send a message to Pedro Eiras (for debug)</description>
